   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "1. which features influence house price the most?\n",
    "   Area of the house\n",
    "   Number of bathrooms\n",
    "   Number of bedrooms\n",
    "   Parking space\n",
    "Among these bathroom and area have the strongest impact on price\n",
    "\n",
    "2. how accurate was your model?\n",
    "\n",
    "   the linear regression model gave moderate accuracy while random forest model performed better\n",
    "\n",
    "   the model predicts house prices reasonably well, but there is still some difference between actual and predicated values\n",
    "\n",
    "3. what surprised you in data?\n",
    "\n",
    "   some smaller houses had higher prices due to better features\n",
    "\n",
    "   features like air conditioning and furnishing status also affect price significantly\n",
    "\n",
    "4. recommendation for real estate business?\n",
    "\n",
    "   use machine learning models to estimate fair house prices\n",
    "\n",
    "   avoid pricing only based on area include all features for better valuation\n",
    "\n",
    "   focus on improving house features like bathrooms, parking,and air conditioning\n",
    "   \n",
    "   \n",
    "   "
   ]
  },
